AGEMENT SYSTEM CASTS AN AFFIDAVIT BALLOT, HE OR SHE SHALL BE RETURNED TO ACTIVE STATUS IN THE STATEWIDE ELECTIONS MANAGEMENT SYSTEM; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."}, "jurisdiction": {"id": "ocd-jurisdiction/country:us/state:ms/government", "name": "Mississippi", "classification": "state", "division_id": "ocd-division/country:us/state:ms"}, "scraped_at": "2026-02-15T08:33:56+00:00", "_id": "11307bc0-0a49-11f1-880d-d2297fa56ca2"}